+`agent.tools` configures a global tool allow/deny policy (deny wins).
+This is applied even when the Docker sandbox is **off**.
+
+Example (disable browser/canvas everywhere):
+```json5
+{
+  agent: {
+    tools: {
+      deny: ["browser", "canvas"]
+    }
+  }
+}
+```
