+## Disabling tools
+
+You can globally allow/deny tools via `agent.tools` in `clawdbot.json`
+(deny wins). This prevents disallowed tools from being sent to providers.
+
+```json5
+{
+  agent: {
+    tools: {
+      deny: ["browser"]
+    }
+  }
+}
+```
